            <div class="today-studio-featured-footer">
              <div class="today-studio-featured-info">
                <div class="today-studio-featured-main">
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-title">STUDIO B</div>
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-price">35€/H • Jusqu'à 10 personnes</div>
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-features">40 m² • Ingénieur son inclus • Acoustique optimisée</div>
                </div>
                <div class="today-studio-featured-description">
