              </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="today-studio-featured-footer">
              <div class="today-studio-featured-info">
                <div class="today-studio-featured-main">
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-title">STUDIO C</div>
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-price">30€/H • Jusqu'à 6 personnes</div>
                  <div class="today-studio-featured-features">25 m² • Ingénieur son inclus • Intimité garantie</div>
