              <span>Gold</span>
            </div>
            <div class="today-fidelite-content">
              <div class="today-fidelite-hours">
                <span class="today-fidelite-number">40</span>
                <span class="today-fidelite-unit">heures</span>
              </div>
              <div class="today-fidelite-discount">
                <span class="today-fidelite-percent">-15%</span>
                <span class="today-fidelite-label">Enregistrement = 29,75€/h<br>Mix/Mastering = 123,25€</span>
